@@TJvExSpeedButton
Summary
  Base class for extended speed buttons.
Description
  TJvExSpeedButton is a base class for classes in the JVCL library that descend from TSpeedButton.
  
  Do not create instances of TJvExSpeedButton. The TJvSpeedButton class provides a generic
  implementation of TJvExSpeedButton. You can also create your own descendant class.

